Login to AWS EC2 Linux instance
login as sudi su
install javajdk package for maven
download apache maven in binary file /opt/maven
wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.8.4/binaries/apache-maven-3.8.4-bin.tar.gz
extact the bainary file
tar -xvzf apache-maven-3.8.4-bin.tar.gz
configure java and maven environment variable in ~/.bash_profile as mentioned
M2_HOME=/opt/maven/apache-maven-3.8.4
M2=$M2_HOME/bin
JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.151-1.b12.amzn2.x86_64
PATH=$PATH:$JAVA_HOME:$M2:$HOME/bin
check mvn version by using mvn -version
Create project using mvn archetype:generate
create changes in index.jsp file and push project to Github
